com.thomsonreuters.upa.valueadd.domainrep.rdm.dictionary

Interface DictionaryRequest

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DictionaryMsg, MsgBase

    public interface DictionaryRequest
extends DictionaryMsg
    The RDM Dictionary Request. Used by an OMM Consumer to request a dictionary from a services that provides it.
    See Also:
    MsgBase, DictionaryMsg
